devFestEvents.name: DevFest 台中
devFestEvents.descText: GDG Taichung (Google Developer Group Taichung) 是以研究 Google 相關技術為主的開發者社群，於每週四晚上聚會，由與會者提供數個 Lightening Talk，並不定期邀請講者分享特定主題、舉辦 Hackthon 或 Workshop 等活動。聚會地點在大台中地區，地點將隨著每次活動發佈。

location.name: 東海大學
location.mapSubTitle: 407台中市西屯區台灣大道四段1727號

devFestEvents.name: DevFest 花蓮
devFestEvents.descText: ''DevFests are community-led, developer events hosted by GDG chapters around the globe focused on community building & learning about Google’s technologies. Each DevFest is inspired by and uniquely tailored to the needs of the developer community and region that hosts it.''
